## Compliance

- **User**: read the README, install for personal use, enjoy.
- **Fork maintainer**: keep this LICENSE + THIRDPARTY/ intact; don't strip
  the non-commercial notice from any release containing D3DMetal.
- **Want to commercialize?** Don't include D3DMetal. Build a calimocho variant
  with only upstream-LGPL components (Wine + vkd3d-proton + DXVK + MoltenVK).
  DX12 perf will be lower, but the license becomes fully permissive.

## Disclaimer

We are not lawyers; nothing here is legal advice. For binding interpretation,
read Apple's full GPTK SLA and consult a qualified attorney.
